Package com.g1.mychess.match.repository

Interface MatchPlayerRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<MatchPlayer,Long>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<MatchPlayer,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<MatchPlayer,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<MatchPlayer,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<MatchPlayer,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<MatchPlayer>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<MatchPlayer,Long>
@Repository public interface MatchPlayerRepository extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<MatchPlayer,Long>
Repository interface for MatchPlayer entity. This interface extends JpaRepository to provide CRUD operations for the MatchPlayer entity. It also includes custom query methods for retrieving match player data based on player ID, match ID, tournament ID, and round number.

      List<MatchPlayer> findByMatch_TournamentIdAndCurrentRound(Long tournamentId, int currentRound)
      Finds all MatchPlayer entities associated with a specific tournament and current round. This method retrieves all match players for a given tournament ID and the current round.
      Parameters:
      tournamentId - The ID of the tournament to find match players for.
      currentRound - The round number to filter the match players by.
      Returns:
      A list of MatchPlayer entities for the given tournament and current round.
